***zm_office_outbreak***
Basicaly I made this map for ZombieHorde, And Zombie Mod, its a balance map, fun to play in, and can also be used as a regular deathmatch, bombsite, there are 3 floors, secrect basement with 2 breakable walls to get out, 2 vent shafts, 1 elevtor shaft, and secrect room on the top floor, So far i am impressed with my map and i hope you guys enjoy it
--------**Wish there was a game mode on this site called Zm for zombie maps only**----

1/32 Players Max
Desgin Mostly For Zombie Mods

Installion
C:/Program Files/Value/Steam/SteamApps/(username)/counter strike source/cstrike/maps

Once Installed Run CounterStrike
